{"tid":1175980,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"艾馬利狠批教授：雲加那支阿仙奴心態疲弱","createTime":"2019-05-29T02:12:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-03T12:48:39.000Z","uid":165817,"like":15,"dislike":87,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"2bdca62e5e045a3a4c3690c6b7315a0880cd838a","tid":1175980,"uid":165817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T02:12:35.000Z","msg":"艾馬利說：「我來的時候，我們改變了一些東西。在前雲加時代，阿仙奴已經很有競爭力，而雲加來了之後，在競爭力的基礎上還增強了球隊的實力，也迎來了阿仙奴的鼎盛時期。」<br />\n<br />\n「但在雲加執教的最後幾年，球隊的競爭心態逐漸減弱，只剩實力了。」<br />\n<br />\n「從其他人身上學到的知識告訴我，球隊不僅要有技術能力強的球員，還需要有那種肯用身體去對抗的球員。若只有技術，很難追趕其他球隊，只有身體質素也是一樣，因此我希望兩者能夠兼備。」<br />\n<br />\n「我們希望一步步來，一年不可能完全做好，但必須縮小和其他球隊的差距。」"},{"pid":"38c4ce40acb146fa863acb4b8ba6f3c76279fbf7","tid":1175980,"uid":14075,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T02:26:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66f656dbb5f7d3f8fc96793bfc7522dc826cf44a","tid":1175980,"uid":52881,"like":75,"dislike":1,"score":74,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T02:27:43.000Z","msg":"拎唔到前四仲咁多嗲"},{"pid":"3401b8b68b20394463556adf7f9fcbe18ef569e5","tid":1175980,"uid":19552,"like":59,"dislike":0,"score":59,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T02:28:29.000Z","msg":"決賽輸撚左請自動躝"},{"pid":"835e5b4cfeccbd8fcea68fd4809b88abd6b0abaf","tid":1175980,"uid":52122,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T02:28:57.000Z","msg":"收嗲啦愛蛇<br />\n爺爺都屌"},{"pid":"b45d6d5f98b40be3e3bec99d9442041f7c747e0c","tid":1175980,"uid":30476,"like":39,"dislike":0,"score":39,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T02:29:18.000Z","msg":"洗撚哂爺爺 d錢 <br />\n仲屌9爺爺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"388835e5da10ba7d3307b702c87aacce8196687d","tid":1175980,"uid":99700,"like":81,"dislike":0,"score":81,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T02:30:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/knUfide.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FknUfide.gif&h=a3537710&